<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kopparakecaripaṉmaṟkku yāṇṭu <num value="23">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>Āvatu <unclear>n</unclear>āḷ <num value="43">4 <g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num> viracoḻa Iḷaṅkoveḷāyiṉa Ātittam tiruvoṟṟiyūraṭikaḷe
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉ piramateyam Īcāṉamaṅkalattu tiruccentuṟaik kaṟṟaḷi parame<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> ra<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku nāṉ vivā<hi rend="grantha">hadakṣi</hi> ṇaiyāka Eramanallūrnampiyāyiṉa
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">bha</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">rudrabha</hi> ṭṭaṉakaiyyil <hi rend="grantha">Uda</hi> kapū<hi rend="grantha">rvva</hi> kañceytu kuṭutta nilamāvatu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Uṟaiyūrkkūṟṟattu Amaṇkuṭi Ūrveliāṉa 3- veliyum Uṇṇi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>lam Oḻiviṉṟi Iṟaiyili ca<hi rend="grantha">ndrādi</hi> ttaval tevatāna(m)māka nir<unclear>o</unclear>ṭu Aṭṭikuṭutteṉ tirucceṉtuṟaip<hi rend="grantha">parameśvara</hi> <supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku Ātittaṉ tiruoṟṟi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yū(r)raṭikaḷeṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Iñilattāl tiruuṇṇāḻikaiyil tirunontāviḷakku 1- kkuk kālceyyāṉapaṭi <num value="12"><g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num> tiruviḷakku Erivatāka Ipparicu tevatā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉañceytu kalme<unclear>lum</unclear> veṭṭuvittukkuṭutteṉ tirucentuṟaip parame<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> ra<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku Ā<hi rend="grantha">di</hi> ttaṉ tiruoṟṟiyūraṭikaḷeṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Itu paṉ<hi rend="grantha">mā he[śvara rakṣai <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*]</hi>
</p>

